{"tid":1462452,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「正視聽」粉紅豬嘴filter係防煙必備裝，咪再9up捉鬼!!","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T06:15:15.000Z","uid":50904,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8cb493ae2f12621995a08f17c6c4b6bee25118","tid":1462452,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"首先「催淚煙」應該正名為刺激性神經化學武器佢主要有效成份係以 晶體  +  有機氣體 方式散播，所以就算煙散左都仲係有毒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n     而且當中啲晶體係最毒嘅，要阻隔啲晶體就一定要有微粒(particulate) filter，3M嘅P100 濾綿個P字就係解 微粒 particulate ，100代表過濾效能係貼近100%<br />\n<br />\n     事實就係3M P100濾綿 209X 系列就係粉色嘅，而防煙頂裝60926 濾罐粉紅果part就內置嘅P100濾綿，唔好問我點解微粒濾綿要整做粉紅色，要問自己問3M  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n    <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LnMHv1T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnMHv1T.png&h=664c9e32&s={SIZE}\" />        </div><br />\n<br />\n點樣有效防煙由6月到依加已經有無數巴絲打出post、前線義士實測，邊個到今日仲走黎出post話粉紅豬嘴係內鬼記認嘅，請問你昏迷左幾耐?<br />\n<br />\n      <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以你班捉鬼敢死隊唔好咁on9啦，如果粉紅豬嘴filter可以用黎，咁保鮮紙都可以捉鬼、麥提莎都可以打鬼啦!</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警非法充公左咁多gear，加埋咁多狗mon post，佢地安插得內鬼入前線，點會唔知戴有粉紅P100濾綿先防到煙?<br />\n<br />\n另外，特別呼籲係amazon/digikey買濾罐嘅人，60921, 60923, 60925, 60928罐效能同60926一樣，邊隻有貨/平就買邊隻<br />\n<br />\n至於只係得600X濾罐嘅人，依加啲過期化武又毒又濃，無P100濾綿係頂唔住架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請立即買返個501 / 502接駁器加 229X / 209X 濾綿接落濾罐度，兩者防煙效能相約但229X濾綿據講係比較透氣可以呼吸得舒服啲<br />\n<br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要有效減低化學武器傷害，豬嘴+氣密鏡+長衫褲  =  呼吸系統 + 眼 + 皮膚防護，三為一體缺一不可呀!  </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔熟書嘅立刻睇返下面嘅整合post/fb page</span></strong><br />\nDgx69210開嘅曼最新防具整合post加google doc攻略<br />\n依加佢研究緊防彈護目鏡，快啲入去學野/幫推/報料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1461702/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1461702/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nDr. Incognito 無名博士<br />\n詳解各種裝個人防護裝備，社會上好多人可能都係出於義憤走上街頭，佢地未必會睇連登post學防煙，快啲入去like&amp; share比其他人知<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDr.Incognito.HK%2F&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=0de76f50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKxzm9S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKxzm9S.jpg&h=a5034f28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後就係，就算義士出核彈、錫春袋我都唔割呀 !</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇武同和理非缺一不可，請唔好將所有義士嘅舉動講成係鬼所做，既然無大台所以每個人必需自己思考每一個舉動係咪合理、係咪對件事有幫助。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有內鬼存在係事實，但沉迷捉鬼只會令「邊個衝邊個就係鬼」嘅心態遮蓋理性，到時唔需要鬼都會令成場運動被瓦解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7b8fc049644a3567fd3448adecf5c27bd4346e","tid":1462452,"uid":50904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"自推10連<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你班捉鬼敢死隊唔好咁on9啦，如果粉紅豬嘴filter可以用黎，咁保鮮紙都可以捉鬼、麥提莎都可以打鬼啦!</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fab3b4215fff80260bf4df897fbde78745eb7c","tid":1462452,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"3efb710f69ac1873c24dbb02c5a8fa8c0a31e84d","tid":1462452,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"6571c16f51cb3d107099864a22af0e7198c1696a","tid":1462452,"uid":50904,"like":0,"disli