itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班捉鬼敢死隊唔好咁on9啦，如果粉紅豬嘴filter可以用黎，咁保鮮紙都可以捉鬼、麥提莎都可以打鬼啦!</span></span>"},{"pid":"e45ddc5d7285c4da8c3221e3a872a3b331be9186","tid":1462452,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"打得太長，自己睇唔到句總結打漏左隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簡單結論:如果粉紅豬嘴filter可以用黎mark鬼，咁保鮮紙都可以捉鬼、麥提莎都可以打鬼啦!</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a49dfa16da23b0d85767f495c346c30b9bf09d","tid":1462452,"uid":168567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa34c995498c7a48560c513895c527419edc622","tid":1462452,"uid":284183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:16:47.000Z","msg":"請問邊到仲有得賣???"},{"pid":"52c1da1c90ae3090893d68f4de89c734e2783ed0","tid":1462452,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa34c995498c7a48560c513895c527419edc622","tid":1462452,"uid":284183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:16:47.000Z","msg":"請問邊到仲有得賣???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"可參考呢個google doc攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=a99e578d\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n出自Dgx69210開嘅最新防具整合post加google doc攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1461702/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1461702/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n留意返，話新填地街五金鋪比係較多，但果邊亦都長期比黑警加便衣mon實，自己留意現場情況"},{"pid":"9519d4ce3803b2e8c46795e1b1b673fb2a03d074","tid":1462452,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"借位一問<br />\n小弟明明係港豬黎<br />\n點解YouTube會推薦左依條片畀我睇嘅?<br />\n依啲野真係好暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_7jiIQOgwtI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_7jiIQOgwtI&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=61b81f04\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_7jiIQOgwtI</a>"}]}